. As discussed in the “Vendor Tools/Analytics on the Website” Section of our Privacy Policy, the Services may rely on advertising technologies that allow for the delivery of relevant content and advertising on the Services, as well as on other websites you visit and other applications you use, and these technologies will collect certain information from your use of the Services to assist in delivering such ads.
Identifiers
